overview.en: MEET.ONE is a EOS block producer candidate team from Singapore, dedicating to be an entrance of EOS ecology. MEET.ONE was elected as a EOS block producer on 15 June 2018. We are committed to being the entrance of EOS ecology and actively participate in the construction of EOS ecology.
overview.zh: MEET.ONE 是来自新加坡的 EOS 超级节点竞选团队，并于2018年6月15日当选 EOS 创世超级节点。致力于成为EOS 生态入口，积极参与 EOS 生态建设。
